# Description
EVE - Isk per Hour is a Windows program that allows players of EVE Online to determine ways to maximize their Isk per Hour through manufacturing, mining, invention, and reverse engineering.

Please use the forums linked above or email <ZifrianEVE@gmail.com> to ask questions, report bugs, or provide feedback and feature requests. Thanks!

# Download
[Get the Windows Installer Here](  http://sourceforge.net/projects/eveiph/files/Eve%20Isk%20per%20Hour%203.1.msi/download)
[Get the Binary Files Here](  http://sourceforge.net/projects/eveiph/files/EVEIPH%20v3.1%20Binaries.zip/download)
